  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK247">
<l>aruḷilārk kavvulaka millai poruḷilārk</l>
<l>kivvulaka millāki yāṅku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As this world is not for those who are without wealth, so that world is not for those who are without kindness.</l>
            </lg>
